39
00:02:32,020 --> 00:02:32,980
You're really rich.

40
00:02:33,540 --> 00:02:34,540
They say

41
00:02:34,780 --> 00:02:36,900
you need to pay more for this letter.

42
00:02:39,060 --> 00:02:39,740
Then this must be

43
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:41,140
something important.

44
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:49,070
[The Elder who's recommended Zhuge Yun
died a month ago. Be wary.]

45
00:02:56,660 --> 00:02:57,820
Should we call off the examination?

46
00:02:57,940 --> 00:02:58,660
It's too late.

47
00:02:58,860 --> 00:02:59,780
Let's go check on Baili Dongjun.

48
00:03:03,860 --> 00:03:04,540
Baili Dongjun!

49
00:03:11,980 --> 00:03:13,260
You guys should have

50
00:03:13,260 --> 00:03:14,220
escaped without me.

51
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:16,020
Now I've distracted him for nothing.

52
00:03:18,340 --> 00:03:19,060
Since we can't escape,

53
00:03:19,540 --> 00:03:20,380
let's fight.

54
00:03:20,740 --> 00:03:21,580
There are four of us.

55
00:03:22,100 --> 00:03:23,500
Do you think we're not strong enough?

56
00:03:24,460 --> 00:03:25,700
Try him

57
00:03:25,740 --> 00:03:26,740
and see.

58
00:03:27,260 --> 00:03:28,820
I may be new to the martial arts world,

59
00:03:29,180 --> 00:03:30,340
but I can tell

60
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:32,020
that he's at the Sovereign Sky Phase.

61
00:03:32,260 --> 00:03:33,500
We're only at the Sturdy Phase.

62
00:03:33,780 --> 00:03:34,940
We're no match for him.

63
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:39,060
You're wrong.

64
00:03:40,060 --> 00:03:40,700
How so?

65
00:03:41,540 --> 00:03:42,620
I'm not at the Sturdy Phase.

66
00:04:00,540 --> 00:04:02,940
