74
00:04:23,020 --> 00:04:23,420
Well...

75
00:04:23,820 --> 00:04:24,380
Dongjun.

76
00:04:24,460 --> 00:04:24,980
What?

77
00:04:31,540 --> 00:04:32,300
I'm also

78
00:04:33,860 --> 00:04:35,100
at Carefree Earth Phase.

79
00:04:37,460 --> 00:04:38,820
