Just now,

84
00:04:59,980 --> 00:05:01,220
you could have abandoned

85
00:05:01,220 --> 00:05:02,020
the kid

86
00:05:02,020 --> 00:05:02,980
with the sword,

87
00:05:03,140 --> 00:05:04,340
yet you did not.

88
00:05:04,900 --> 00:05:06,700
I'm impressed.

89
00:05:07,340 --> 00:05:08,660
The point of the test

90
00:05:08,780 --> 00:05:10,220
is to impress me.

91
00:05:10,980 --> 00:05:12,580
If you could actually

92
00:05:12,780 --> 00:05:14,020
beat me,

93
00:05:14,460 --> 00:05:15,580
there's no need for you
to learn skills here.

94
00:05:16,020 --> 00:05:16,660
You'd become

95
00:05:16,660 --> 00:05:17,780
a master then.

96
00:05:18,340 --> 00:05:19,100
Remember

97
00:05:19,340 --> 00:05:20,780
what happened today.

98
00:05:21,140 --> 00:05:22,140
No matter what,

99
00:05:22,700 --> 00:05:24,340
never abandon your companions.

100
00:05:26,900 --> 00:05:27,700
I'll remember what you said.

101
00:05:29,220 --> 00:05:30,140
I, Yujia, will remember your lesson.

102
00:05:30,900 --> 00:05:31,780
Yujia?

103
00:05:32,140 --> 00:05:33,220
What a stupid name.

104
00:05:36,540 --> 00:05:37,700
I told you to watch out.

105
00:05:42,020 --> 00:05:42,980
Sorry, sir.

106
00:05:43,580 --> 00:05:45,220
Here's another tip.

107
00:05:46,100 --> 00:05:47,700
You won't find

108
00:05:48,220 --> 00:05:49,460
what you're looking for

109
