114
00:05:56,460 --> 00:05:58,780
will you find the answer.

115
00:05:59,540 --> 00:06:01,140
Time is of the essence.

116
00:06:02,260 --> 00:06:02,980
Go.

117
00:06:07,220 --> 00:06:07,980
Thank you, sir.

118
00:06:12,700 --> 00:06:13,300
Thanks.

119
00:06:14,860 --> 00:06:15,620
