126
00:06:44,580 --> 00:06:45,740
That weird old man

127
00:06:45,980 --> 00:06:46,860
actually thought

128
00:06:46,980 --> 00:06:47,420
I was going

129
00:06:47,420 --> 00:06:48,580
to break the sword

130
00:06:48,940 --> 00:06:50,020
and stopped me with strong power.

131
00:06:50,540 --> 00:06:51,660
