132
00:06:57,460 --> 00:06:58,300
I'll heal you

133
00:06:58,500 --> 00:06:58,940
in a jiffy.

134
00:07:00,580 --> 00:07:01,340
How long will it take?

135
00:07:02,020 --> 00:07:03,380
At least an hour or so.

136
00:07:03,740 --> 00:07:05,380
We need to treat his wound at once.

137
00:07:05,780 --> 00:07:06,420
If we run into

138
00:07:06,420 --> 00:07:07,300
Zhuge Yun

139
00:07:07,340 --> 00:07:08,100
with one man down,

140
00:07:08,260 --> 00:07:09,020
