141
00:07:09,420 --> 00:07:10,260
I'll stand guard for you.

142
00:07:34,580 --> 00:07:37,020
You sure know a lot of tricks.

143
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:39,900
I've died way too many times.

144
00:07:42,380 --> 00:07:43,140
Concentrate.

145
00:07:57,100 --> 00:07:57,860
Isn't this great?

146
00:07:58,820 --> 00:07:59,740
