147
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:01,980
A group of exceptional youths

148
00:08:02,620 --> 00:08:03,740
gathered

149
00:08:03,820 --> 00:08:04,820
in such a magnificent

150
00:08:04,820 --> 00:08:06,060
and big city,

151
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:07,780
fighting side by side

152
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:11,180
and healing each other under one roof.

153
00:08:15,700 --> 00:08:16,740
It's

154
00:08:16,780 --> 00:08:17,940
a beautiful thing.

155
00:08:25,660 --> 00:08:27,300
If you guys hadn't shown up...

156
00:08:28,420 --> 00:08:29,580
There should be

157
00:08:29,660 --> 00:08:31,340
