162
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:41,340
One of them

163
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:43,140
is the head disciple of Lyu Suzhen,

164
00:08:43,180 --> 00:08:43,940
Wang Yixing,

165
00:08:44,220 --> 00:08:45,420
not Zhao Yujia.

166
00:08:45,940 --> 00:08:46,540
However,

167
00:08:46,740 --> 00:08:47,500
given Mr. Lyu's ties

168
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:48,740
with Mr. Li,

169
00:08:48,980 --> 00:08:51,380
Mr. Li already knew about it.

170
00:08:51,780 --> 00:08:52,980
It's no surprise.

171
00:08:55,020 --> 00:08:56,300
Not only Zhao Yujia,

172
00:08:56,660 --> 00:08:57,580
there are others as well.

173
00:08:58,380 --> 00:08:59,380
Unfortunately,

174
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:00,740
we're too late.

175
00:09:01,340 --> 00:09:02,140
They've already left.

176
00:09:05,220 --> 00:09:05,780
Little Master.

177
00:09:08,140 --> 00:09:09,140
We found a team

178
00:09:09,260 --> 00:09:10,060
in an alley.

179
00:09:10,420 --> 00:09:11,220
All four candidates

180
00:09:11,220 --> 00:09:11,860
