187
00:09:22,540 --> 00:09:24,460
Baixiao Hall's tip is seldom wrong.

188
00:09:25,740 --> 00:09:26,540
Let's go check it out.

189
00:09:29,860 --> 00:09:30,820
Zhuge Yun?

190
00:09:31,540 --> 00:09:32,980
Of the Zhuge Family?

191
00:09:34,980 --> 00:09:35,780
I'll come with you.

192
00:09:46,820 --> 00:09:48,860
Three of the candidates
died horrendously.

193
00:09:49,660 --> 00:09:50,580
When we discovered them,

194
00:09:50,620 --> 00:09:51,340
