would do such a thing?

198
00:10:04,500 --> 00:10:05,100
What grudge did he have

199
00:10:05,100 --> 00:10:05,940
against them?

200
00:10:05,980 --> 00:10:06,700
Why did he

201
00:10:07,340 --> 00:10:08,620
kill the innocent?

202
00:10:11,780 --> 00:10:13,340
Zhuge Yun died in a different manner.

203
00:10:13,740 --> 00:10:15,180
There are fewer wounds on his body.

204
00:10:18,020 --> 00:10:18,540
This way.

205
00:10:31,980 --> 00:10:32,740
He's dead.

206
00:10:39,420 --> 00:10:40,300
I got it.

207
00:10:41,020 --> 00:10:42,380
The culprit

208
00:10:42,460 --> 00:10:43,420
