211
00:10:46,540 --> 00:10:47,660
receive a more merciful death

212
00:10:47,700 --> 00:10:48,420
than the others?

213
00:10:48,980 --> 00:10:49,460
Now is not the time

214
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:50,740
for your nonsense.

215
00:10:51,420 --> 00:10:52,820
Get the coroner at once.

216
00:10:53,940 --> 00:10:54,540
Is he really

217
00:10:54,540 --> 00:10:55,780
Zhuge Yun?

218
00:11:05,580 --> 00:11:06,340
That's...

219
00:11:06,620 --> 00:11:07,820
