about Zhuge Yun?

224
00:11:22,380 --> 00:11:22,860
No.

225
00:11:23,620 --> 00:11:25,020
We had doubts

226
00:11:25,020 --> 00:11:25,940
about his identity,

227
00:11:25,980 --> 00:11:27,220
but what he used

228
00:11:27,300 --> 00:11:28,900
is undoubtedly Qimen Dunjia Arts.

229
00:11:30,860 --> 00:11:31,660
I think

230
00:11:32,420 --> 00:11:33,820
