very complicated.

234
00:11:40,860 --> 00:11:41,860
Interesting.

235
00:11:43,060 --> 00:11:44,460
You don't get to decide

236
00:11:45,700 --> 00:11:47,340
whether we'll show up.

237
00:11:47,620 --> 00:11:48,700
It's indeed Lord Wuzuo.

238
00:11:49,140 --> 00:11:50,140
And this time,

239
00:11:50,740 --> 00:11:52,140
