240
00:11:52,660 --> 00:11:53,580
Zhuge Yun?

241
00:11:56,060 --> 00:11:56,540
No.

242
00:11:56,940 --> 00:11:58,180
A young man like Zhuge Yun

243
00:11:58,660 --> 00:11:59,580
could not possibly

244
00:11:59,580 --> 00:12:00,860
emanate that kind of energy.

245
00:12:01,140 --> 00:12:01,940
Who are you?

246
00:12:02,540 --> 00:12:04,140
It's none of your business.

247
00:12:05,660 --> 00:12:07,460
You're not our target.

248
00:12:11,060 --> 00:12:11,980
Keep healing him.

249
00:12:12,860 --> 00:12:14,620
I'll take care of this.

250
00:12:14,780 --> 00:12:15,140
All right.

251
00:12:16,540 --> 00:12:17,660
A nobody like you?

252
00:12:17,780 --> 00:12:19,180
You're out

253
00:12:19,220 --> 00:12:19,860
of your depth.

254
00:12:34,540 --> 00:12:35,740
A nobody?

255
00:12:43,540 --> 00:12:44,340
This is...

256
00:12:44,620 --> 00:12:45,540
Between creation and destruction

257
00:12:45,660 --> 00:12:46,580
lies a calamity.

258
00:12:46,860 --> 00:12:48,060
Before the world is formed

259
00:12:48,220 --> 00:12:49,620
lies infinite calamity.

260
00:12:49,740 --> 00:12:51,500
It's called
the Infinite Sword technique.

261
00:12:51,900 --> 00:12:53,900
You're not Zhao Yujia.

262
00:12:54,020 --> 00:12:55,380
You can impersonate Zhuge Yun

263
00:12:55,540 --> 00:12:56,820
but I can't impersonate Zhao Yujia?

264
00:12:57,060 --> 00:12:58,780
That's right, I'm not him.

265
00:12:59,260 --> 00:13:00,340
I'm the head disciple

266
00:13:00,420 --> 00:13:02,780
of Lyu Suzhen of Mount Wangcheng,

267
00:13:02,940 --> 00:13:03,380
Wang

268
00:13:03,620 --> 00:13:04,140
Yi

269
00:13:04,260 --> 00:13:04,860
xing.

270
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:58,900
[Yueluo, 32nd Division
of Tianqi Royal Academy]

271
00:13:58,900 --> 00:13:59,820
Your future disciple

272
00:13:59,820 --> 00:14:01,060
is up against a strong foe.

273
00:14:01,500 --> 00:14:02,620
He could die at any second

274
00:14:03,620 --> 00:14:04,860
yet you're sitting here drinking

275
00:14:05,260 --> 00:14:06,180
and yawning?

276
00:14:08,540 --> 00:14:10,500
First of all, this is Tianqi City.

277
00:14:10,620 --> 00:14:12,620
Martial artists are a dime a dozen

278
00:14:12,660 --> 00:14:14,700
and capable martial artists
are everywhere.

279
00:14:15,380 --> 00:14:17,060
There's always

280
00:14:17,220 --> 00:14:18,540
someone stronger.

281
00:14:19,100 --> 00:14:19,860
And

282
00:14:20,900 --> 00:14:22,540
I'm the strongest of them all.

283
00:14:22,860 --> 00:14:23,620
I

284
00:14:23,820 --> 00:14:25,380
am number one!

285
00:14:34,860 --> 00:14:36,340
What's taking the candidates so long?

286
00:14:36,340 --> 00:14:37,100
I'm tired.

287
00:14:38,140 --> 00:14:39,420
Their opponent

288
00:14:39,740 --> 00:14:40,820
is no ordinary man.

289
00:14:42,980 --> 00:14:44,700
There's no such thing
as an ordinary opponent.

290
00:14:45,180 --> 00:14:46,540
There are two kinds of enemies,

291
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:47,540
those

